## Research Lifecycle Phases

| Phase | Skills | Purpose |
|-------|--------|---------|
| 1. Acquisition | ingest-source, batch-ingest, web-research | Bring new sources into the wiki |
| 2. Compilation | update-entities, update-concepts, cross-reference | Build and maintain wiki pages |
| 3. Analysis | query-wiki, generate-comparison, adversarial-review | Extract insights from the wiki |
| 4. Synthesis | compile-output, generate-slides, export-report | Create deliverables from wiki content |
| Maintenance | lint-wiki, reindex, stats | Keep the wiki healthy |
